<Configuration> change these in code

CRC_WIDTH
  the width of CRC-x
  allow 8~32

POLYNOMIAL
  the CRC divisor

REFLECT_IO
  set 1 to reflect the input and output

INIT_VALUE
  initial value of CRC

XOR_MASK
  XOR the result by what value


<Commands>

hexdecimal digits
  input data

?
  dump data

-
  clear data

#
  calculate CRC

&
  print CRC lookup table

@
  calculate CRC, with lookup table
  
